.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-UPTIME-PCT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-uptime-pct \- FEAT-2035 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-uptime-pct
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2035).
.PP
Computes uptime percentage per channel from CLN peer channel data.
Returns 0 when lifetime data is unavailable.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
